{{Info |body =
Not available in Confluence cloud editor. Migration example comes from the script.
}}
The Gallery macro displayed all images attached to a page as a grid of thumbnails. Clicking an image opened a full‑screen viewer with slideshow navigation.
It was part of the legacy editor and worked only on pages created before Atlassian’s editor overhaul. __NOTOC__
